This paper belongs to the computer science sub-category of security and privacy (cs.CR) as it discusses a specific attack on the anonymity network Tor. The paper also involves network measurements and machine learning techniques, which could fall under the sub-categories of networking and internet architecture (cs.NI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the potential for information leakage, which could fall under the sub-categories of cryptography and security (cs.CY) and software engineering (cs.SE).
